comments: Turner (IND) makes hand on ball contact with Embiid (PHI) that dislodges the ball during Embiid's shot attempt.
Richardson (PHI) reaches in and makes contact with the ball during Oladipo's (IND) drive.
Neto (PHI) makes contact with the ball and cleanly steals it from Oladipo (IND)  during the loose ball.
Embiid (PHI) slightly extends two hands into Oladipo's (IND) body but the marginal contact does not affect his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Simmons (PHI) takes a dribble and initiates contact to Turner's (IND) chest but Turner absorbs the marginal contact.
Simmons (PHI) gathers the ball and lifts his pivot  foot as he hops prior to his shot attempt.
Turner (IND) makes contact with the ball during Simmons' (PHI) shot attempt near the rim.
Neto (PHI) reaches in and makes contact with the ball, the following contact to Oladipo's (IND) arm is marginal.
Richardson (PHI) initiates contact to Holiday (IND) during his dribble that affects his SQBR.
Simmons (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position on Warren (IND) as he splits the two defenders, the leg contact that occurs is incidental. Harris (PHI) avoids making contact to Warren's arm.
Turner (IND) dislodges Embiid (PHI) while both players attempt to retrieve the loose ball.
Simmons (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during Warren's (IND) jump shot attempt.
Sampson (IND) and Embiid (PHI) briefly engage in marginal arm to arm contact prior to separating off ball.
